@startuml
' Deployment and Interaction Diagram for MercadoLink B2B
' Shows infrastructure, components, and key user interactions

' Nodes
node "User Device" as user {
    [Web Browser]
}

node "Docker Host" as docker {
    node "Container: mercadolink-b2b" as container {
        [Spring Boot Application] as springApp
        [Embedded H2 Database] as h2db
    }
    artifact "mercadolink-b2b.jar" as jar
}

node "Storage" as storage {
    [Persistent Volume: mercadolink-data] as volume
}

' Deployments
jar -> container : deployed
container ..> volume : mounts volume at /data

' Components inside container
springApp ..> h2db : uses for persistence

' Communication
user -> springApp : HTTP (port 8080) [Serves static React app and REST API]

' Key Interaction Flows (as notes)
note right of springApp
    Login Flow:
    1. Browser -> /api/v1/auth/login (POST)
    2. AuthController -> AuthService
    3. AuthService validates credentials
    4. Returns JWT to browser
    5. Browser stores JWT for subsequent requests
end note

note right of springApp
    Product Fetch Flow:
    1. Browser -> /api/v1/productos (GET) with JWT
    2. ProductoController -> ProductoRepository
    3. Returns active products list
    4. Browser renders product catalog
end note

@enduml